name: P.Y.V.
description:
P.Y.V. or Pretty Young Vintage is both a tribute to one of our favorite melodies from the late King of Pop and our muses that can be found hiding in their natural habitat of the VIP or amongst the lasers on the smoke-screened dance floor. Proclaim your status with our sexy double dyed burnout deep V-neck. Supersoft black 50/50 cotton/poly 30s fabric with pink waterbased silkscreen print. Short sleeve tee with longer fashion fit body.

High Point Shoulder Length	        26.5" 27.0" 27.5"
Bust 1" Below Armhole     	        15.5" 16.5" 17.5"

name: Carpe Noctem - Womens
description:
"Carpe Noctem," Latin for "Seize the Night" inspires one to live life to the fullest and satisfy one's nocturnal desires, whether it be in the streets of Paris or the beaches of Rio. Moonlight, like the ever escaping bubbles from champagne, is a fickle thing and one should harness its energy before it slips away...


Black 100% 40s combed ring-spun sheer cotton jersey. Scoop neck t-shirt with longer fashion body fit. Waterbased silkscreen (softhand feel) on front with BACCHUS text embroidered in purple on back.


Garment Specification_________S____M___L___ 
High Point Shoulder	        26.375" 27.0" 28.25" Length
Bust 1" Below Armhole     	        14.0" 15.0" 16.0"

name: Harlot Aficionado
description:
Bacchus was known as a seducer, the original playboy who stole the hearts of the gods and humans alike. Let your style reflect the taste for one of the finer things in life.


Slim fit tee. Charcoal 100% combed ring-spun sheer cotton jersey. Set-In collar with side seams. Waterbased silkscreen (softhand feel) on front with BACCHUS text embroidered in red on back.
